data.description: This beautiful new home is a real gem, eight months new. It boasts a spacious backyard, which has been significantly upgraded. $30,000+ in pavers, landscaping, patio cover, and epoxy-coated garage floor. The home offers three bedrooms, along with a small loft that can serve a variety of purposes. Another enticing feature of this property it comes with all appliances included, making moving in and getting settled a breeze and custom paint in which builders do not offer without a hefty price. It's perfectly situated, offering proximity to shopping, restaurants, parks, and recreational opportunities. Plus, easy access to freeways ensures that you're well-connected to the rest of the valley. In conclusion, this home is a must-see for anyone in the market. Its combination of new construction, outdoor upgrades, versatile living spaces, and a convenient location make it a compelling opportunity not to be missed. Reach out and schedule a viewing soon before this opportunity is gone.
